n":"carret","display_top_border":true,"open":false,"content":"<p><strong>Instant Volume Boost<\/strong><br\/><br\/> – No need for blow dryers or curling irons, reducing the risk of heat damage.<br\/><br\/> – Designed to hold without pulling, tugging, or causing breakage.<br\/><br\/> – Easy to wear during your routine, whether you're getting ready or multitasking.<br\/><br\/> – Durable design makes it perfect for everyday use and styling on the go.<\/p>","page":"","margin_top":0,"margin_bottom":0}},"collapsible_tab_WYG8GJ":{"type":"collapsible_tab","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Recommended by Dermatologists","heading_size":"small","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"collapse_icon":"carret","display_top_border":true,"open":false,"content":"<p>Officially recommended by dermatologists, the Nifora bio-collagen mask.<\/p><p>This mask is specially formulated to hydrate, tighten fine lines, and improve skin elasticity—your key to radiant, healthy skin.<\/p><p>Trust the expertise and enjoy the benefits of a youthful glow.<\/p>","page":"","margin_top":0,"margin_bottom":0}},"collapsible_tab_QnkEdx":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"How does it work?","heading_size":"small","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"collapse_icon":"carret","display_top_border":true,"open":false,"content":"<h3>How Does It Work?<\/h3><p>The volumizing hair clip tool is designed to gently lift the roots of your hair to create natural volume without the need for heat or backcombing. Simply clip the tool into clean, dry or slightly damp hair at the crown or desired area. Leave it in for 5 to 15 minutes while you continue your routine—such as doing your makeup or getting dressed. Once removed, your hair will have added lift and bounce, ready to be styled as desired.<\/p><p>It’s a quick and easy way to achieve salon-like volume with zero damage.<\/p>","page":"","margin_top":24,"margin_bottom":0}},"collapsible_tab_kwzWVt":{"type":"collapsible_tab","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Ingredients","heading_size":"small","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"collapse_icon":"carret","display_top_border":true,"open":false,"content":"<ul><li><strong>Triple Peptide Power<\/strong> – Boosts collagen & elastin production for <strong>firmer, more youthful skin<\/strong>.<\/li><li><strong>Acetyl Hexapeptide-8 (Argireline)<\/strong> – Known as <strong>\"Botox in a jar\"<\/strong>, this powerful peptide <strong>reduces fine lines & wrinkles.<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Centella Asiatica<\/strong> – Strengthens the <strong>skin barrier<\/strong>, making it perfect for <strong>sensitive, dry, or aging skin<\/strong>.<\/li><li><strong>Tremella Mushroom Extract<\/strong> – Holds <strong>5X more water than hyaluronic acid<\/strong>, ensuring <strong>intense hydration<\/strong> without irritation.<\/li><\/ul>","page":"","margin_top":24,"margin_bottom":0}},"collapsible_tab_QGc8Kr":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Shipping & Delivery","heading_size":"small","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"collapse_icon":"carret","display_top_border":true,"open":false,"content":"<p><strong>Processing Time:<\/strong><br\/>Once your order is placed, please allow 124 hours for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br\/><br\/><strong>Shipping Time:<\/strong><br\/>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 4-8 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br\/><br\/><strong>Tracking Information:<\/strong><br\/>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.<\/p>","page":"","margin_top":24,"margin_bottom":0}},"collapsible_tab_8h6X4m":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Return & Exchange Policy","heading_size":"small","icon":"check_box","filled_icon":false,"collapse_icon":"carret","display_top_border":true,"open":false,"content":"<p>We want you to be fully satisfied with your purchase! 