 longer-lasting results, you can use a light styling spray to keep the volume intact.<\/em><\/p>"}},"text_Xpzxzp":{"type":"text","settings":{"question":"Is the hair root clip suitable for all hair types?","answer":"<p>Yes, the hair root clip works on all hair types—whether your hair is short, long, thick, or fine. It adds volume and lift to any style.<\/p>"}},"text_BDtRac":{"type":"text","settings":{"question":"Can I use the clip on wet hair?","answer":"<p>It’s best to use the clip on hair that’s about 70-80% dry. This allows the clip to work effectively without damaging your hair.<\/p>"}},"text_UdqCJ3":{"type":"text","settings":{"question":"Will the clip damage my hair?","answer":"<p>No, the hair root clip is designed to be gentle on your hair. It doesn’t require any heat, so it won’t cause damage or leave marks on your hair.<\/p>"}},"text_3TN8mq":{"type":"text","settings":{"question":"How long will the volume last?","answer":"<p>The volume lasts for hours, but for longer-lasting results, you can use a styling spray to set your hair after removing the clip.<\/p>"}},"text_Y9yyii":{"type":"text","settings":{"question":"Can I use the clip every day?","answer":"<p>Absolutely! The clip is designed for daily use and is gentle enough to incorporate into your regular styling routine.<\/p>"}},"text_ntbDgy":{"type":"text","settings":{"question":"What are the delivery times?","answer":"<p><strong>Processing Time: <\/strong>Once your order is placed, please allow 1 business day for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br\/><br\/><strong>Shipping Time: <\/strong>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 3-5 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br\/><br\/><strong>Tracking Information: <\/strong>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_kGtL6b","text_Xpzxzp","text_BDtRac","tex